1
00:00:59,340 --> 00:01:01,056
Good morning, honey.

2
00:01:04,190 --> 00:01:05,464
Good morning.

3
00:01:17,850 --> 00:01:19,112
Wait...

4
00:01:19,940 --> 00:01:21,216
Why?

5
00:01:21,480 --> 00:01:23,352
I have to go to work now.

6
00:01:23,920 --> 00:01:25,848
Just a little bit.

7
00:01:26,070 --> 00:01:26,872
No.

8
00:01:45,800 --> 00:01:53,848
Ohh... I don’t want to go to work at all.

9
00:01:55,290 --> 00:01:57,096
Get up now.

10
00:02:00,192 --> 00:02:01,672
I don't want to go.

11
00:02:02,464 --> 00:02:04,460
You're going to be late.

12
00:02:04,744 --> 00:02:06,008
Get up now.

13
00:02:08,610 --> 00:02:11,784
I really don't want to go to work...

14
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:14,952
Fine, I’m going.

15
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:09,456
Holy shit!

16
00:05:16,816 --> 00:05:18,144
Go ahead and order whatever you want.

17
00:05:18,384 --> 00:05:19,896
It’s on me.

18
00:05:21,040 --> 00:05:23,552
I’ll take everything on the menu!

19
00:05:41,450 --> 00:05:44,752
Hey! calm down.

20
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:46,288
What the hell?

21
00:05:47,560 --> 00:05:49,560
What is Ran even doing?

22
00:05:50,330 --> 00:05:51,768
Does she have any idea what he’s doing?

23
00:05:52,930 --> 00:05:56,536
Yeah, I’m totally shocked too.

24
00:05:56,584 --> 00:05:58,960
I don’t know what Chat is thinking.

25
00:06:04,380 --> 00:06:05,696
So what do we do?

26
00:06:06,500 --> 00:06:07,576
Do we stop them?

27
00:06:08,500 --> 00:06:10,288
And what if they don't admit to it?

28
00:06:11,496 --> 00:06:13,500
It’ll be so awkward we won't be able to face them.

29
00:06:13,528 --> 00:06:15,944
But  you know this is wrong.

30
00:06:15,968 --> 00:06:17,744
I know.

31
00:06:22,910 --> 00:06:28,960
Alright... tomorrow, let’s go talk to Chat and Ranya together.

32
00:06:29,980 --> 00:06:30,744
It’s good,

33
00:06:32,740 --> 00:06:35,424
Cheers!

34
00:06:42,300 --> 00:06:43,504
Don’t be a wimp.

35
00:06:49,500 --> 00:06:50,880
Slow down.

36
00:06:51,060 --> 00:06:52,080
No.

37
00:06:57,860 --> 00:06:59,512
Can I get another one, sis?

38
00:07:05,510 --> 00:07:07,528
Take it easy, girl. My wallet can’t handle this anymore.

39
00:07:08,020 --> 00:07:09,872
Didn't you tell me to order whatever I wanted?

40
00:07:11,870 --> 00:07:12,832
Fine. Order whatever you want.

41
00:07:14,830 --> 00:07:15,760
Hey, waiter! Give us everything in the shop!

42
00:07:15,808 --> 00:07:17,128
You’re so weak.
